OL,3,CSwindon South MP Heidi Alexander
OL,4,Cappointed Transport Secretary
OL,6,FHeidi Alexander has been appointed
OL,7,FTransport Secretary after the
OL,8,Fresignation of Louise Haigh over a
OL,9,Fundisclosed criminal conviction.
OL,11,FDowning Street announced the
OL,12,Fappointment on X on Friday 29
OL,13,FNovember. Ms Alexander had been made a
OL,14,Fjustice minister after Labour won the
OL,15,Felection in July.
OL,17,FIt comes after Louise Haigh resigned
OL,18,Ffrom the role after it emerged she had
OL,19,Fincorrectly told police that a work
OL,20,Fmobile phone was stolen in 2013.
